    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escaping Diddler</strong> is a dark, stealth-based survival game where your mission is to outsmart the twisted host of a disturbing house party. As you navigate through &quot;Diddler’s Backyard&quot; you’ll need to find and steal bottles of baby oil. But it won’t be easy—Diddler is actively hunting you down, and if you’re caught, it’s game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your moves carefully, stay hidden, and escape his clutches before it's too late. With more maps to come, you’ll need to master your stealth skills to survive this high-stakes game of cat and mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you escape or become his next victim?</p>",
